                         <div class=\"col-md-12 view-all-collection-button-new\">\n                                                               <a id=\"view-more-3bhk-designs\" href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/3bhk-interior-design\/\">View More 3 BHK Designs > <\/a>\n                                                      <\/div>\n                     <\/div>\n                  <\/div>\n               <\/div>\n               <\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">The Chic Living Room<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The vision was to keep the living room style minimalistic and modern. Since the clients desired a clutter-free space, the Design Cafe team installed a simple TV unit with earthy colours. Artefacts were used to highlight the room and bring in some oomph. The room\u2019s large L-shaped window posed the challenge of too much natural light. A light-colour curtain was used for the windows to prevent the room from getting dark yet bring in enough light. Artificial lighting was used in the periphery of the room to create a cosy ambience which along with natural light and a striking chandelier helped achieve a desired look.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/26211055\/living-room-good-interior-designers-in-bangalore.jpg\" alt=\"The earthy colour living room designed with a tv unit, sofa and centre table, interior designers in Whitefield.\" class=\"wp-image-19754\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/26211055\/living-room-good-interior-designers-in-bangalore.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/26211055\/living-room-good-interior-designers-in-bangalore-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/26211055\/living-room-good-interior-designers-in-bangalore-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/26211055\/living-room-good-interior-designers-in-bangalore-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">The look of the room is elevated by the light-colour curtain and the attractive chandelier.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">The Welcoming Dining Area<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The living, cooking and dining spaces have been planned in an open design. A partition was installed by good <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/cities\/interior-designers-bangalore\/\">interior designers in Bangalore<\/a> between the living room and dining area that works as a showcase as well. A breakfast table was placed between the living room and kitchen. This table not only helps demarcate two areas but also provides a storage option in the kitchen.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/26211031\/dining-room-interiors-in-whitefield.jpg\" alt=\"Dining area between living and kitchen with a round dining table and chairs look chic, good interior designers in Whitefield, Bangalore.\" class=\"wp-image-19750\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/26211031\/dining-room-interiors-in-whitefield.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/26211031\/dining-room-interiors-in-whitefield-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/26211031\/dining-room-interiors-in-whitefield-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/26211031\/dining-room-interiors-in-whitefield-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">The open design of the living, cooking and dining areas helps create a spacious look.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Roomy Kitchen<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The intention behind the kitchen design was to allow easy movement and create plenty of space for groceries and appliances. The breakfast table is a clever addition that ensures there is an extra counter with storage. Design Cafe\u2019s interior designers in Whitefield, Bangalore, chose to go for a stone-textured laminate. To balance the look of the laminate, the team opted for a neutral white shade. Pretty <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/moroccan-tiles-design\/\">Moroccan tiles<\/a> were used for the dado wall that lifts the ambience of the open kitchen.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/26211049\/kitchen-low-budget-interior-designers-in-bangalore.jpg\" alt=\"Kitchen with Moroccan tiles backsplash and stone-textured cabinet designed at low budget interior designers in Whitefield, Bangalore.\" class=\"wp-image-19753\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/26211049\/kitchen-low-budget-interior-designers-in-bangalore.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/26211049\/kitchen-low-budget-interior-designers-in-bangalore-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/26211049\/kitchen-low-budget-interior-designers-in-bangalore-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/26211049\/kitchen-low-budget-interior-designers-in-bangalore-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">The white neutral colour works well with the heavy laminate shades to create a sublime vibe in the kitchen.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">The Quaint Master Bedroom<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/master-bedroom-design-ideas\/\">master bedroom<\/a> had a niche in the corner which Design Cafe\u2019s team of experts utilised to create a private study for the homeowners. The study has space for storage as well. Cement finish laminates have been used to give the room a rustic feel. Olive green curtains with an elegant wallpaper complete the look of this space.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/26211102\/master-bedroom-best-interior-designers-in-whitefield.jpg\" alt=\"Master bedroom cum study area designed with an elegant wallpaper gives a rustic feel, best interior designers in Whitefield.\" class=\"wp-image-19755\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/26211102\/master-bedroom-best-interior-designers-in-whitefield.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/26211102\/master-bedroom-best-interior-designers-in-whitefield-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/26211102\/master-bedroom-best-interior-designers-in-whitefield-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/26211102\/master-bedroom-best-interior-designers-in-whitefield-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">The study area in the corner niche is an intelligent touch that makes optimum use of space.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">The Walk-In Wardrobe<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The master bedroom had a narrow space for a walk-in wardrobe. Design Cafe\u2019s experts chose a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/sliding-wardrobe-design-ideas\/\">sliding wardrobe<\/a> with a light-coloured laminate. A large dressing mirror makes the spaces look bigger.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/26211108\/walk-in-wardrobe-interior-design-in-whitefield.jpg\" alt=\"Narrow space for a walk-in wardrobe with sliding door laminated in a light colour looks warm, interior design in Whitefield.\" class=\"wp-image-19756\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/26211108\/walk-in-wardrobe-interior-design-in-whitefield.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/26211108\/walk-in-wardrobe-interior-design-in-whitefield-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/26211108\/walk-in-wardrobe-interior-design-in-whitefield-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/26211108\/walk-in-wardrobe-interior-design-in-whitefield-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">The walk-in wardrobe deftly uses available space to integrate customisations.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Wooden Themed Bedroom<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This bedroom sports a rich wooden theme that uplifts the vibe in the house. Cove lighting helps illuminate the space while natural light streaming in through the window creates a warm atmosphere. The bed looks extremely comfortable and the green plants on the side table add contrast.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/26211025\/bedroom-interior-designers-in-whitefield-bangalore.jpg\" alt=\"Bedroom interiors in Whitefield with wooden theme and dressing table made from wood creates a rustic feel.\" class=\"wp-image-19749\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/26211025\/bedroom-interior-designers-in-whitefield-bangalore.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/26211025\/bedroom-interior-designers-in-whitefield-bangalore-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/26211025\/bedroom-interior-designers-in-whitefield-bangalore-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/26211025\/bedroom-interior-designers-in-whitefield-bangalore-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">The wallpaper in this bedroom is a work of art that mesmerises<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Are you interested in employing good interior designers in Bangalore to decorate your home the way Poonam and Yashwant have? Then why don\u2019t you give us a call! We will be happy to help you turn your imagination into exactly how your dream home looks and feels. Give us a call today if you are on the lookout for interior designers in Whitefield.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Are You Looking For Best Interior Designers?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/cities\/interior-designers-hyderabad\/\">Best Interior Designers in Hyderabad<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/cities\/interior-designers-mumbai\/\">Best Interior Designers in Mumbai<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\"><\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> <\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\